name: samtools
description: Tools (written in C using htslib) for manipulating next-generation sequencing data.

name: sambamba
description: Tools for working with SAM/BAM data.

name: bwa
description: Burrow-Wheeler Aligner for short-read alignment (see minimap2 for long-read alignment).

name: mosdepth
description: fast BAM/CRAM depth calculation for WGS, exome, or targeted sequencing.

name: samblaster
description: samblaster: a tool to mark duplicates and extract discordant and split reads from sam files.
